<%= render "shared/banner" %>
<div id="home-container">
  <div class="container div-margin-top" id="section-1">
    <div class="row div-margin-top homepage-row" id="anchor-1">
      <div class="col-sm-6">

        <%= image_tag "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1519389950473-47ba0277781c?ixlib=rb-0.3.5&ixid=eyJhcHBfaWQiOjEyMDd9&s=47d2b1f32cc05c976af4a39256e01cba&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1350&q=80", class: "home-image"  %>

      </div>
      <div class="col-sm-offset-1 col-sm-5">
        <h1>Why</h1>
        <h3>Have you ever thought about how much companies know about you?</h3>

        <div class="bullets-flex">
          <div><i class="fa fa-circle bullets-icon"></i></div>
          <div class="bullets-text"><p>Do you know exactly what they know?</p></div>
        </div>

        <div class="bullets-flex">
          <div><i class="fa fa-circle bullets-icon"></i></div>
          <div class="bullets-text"><p>What are they using your data for?</p></div>
        </div>

        <div class="bullets-flex">
          <div><i class="fa fa-circle bullets-icon"></i></div>
          <div class="bullets-text"><p>Do they give it to others?</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bullets-flex">
          <div><i class="fa fa-circle bullets-icon"></i></div>
          <div class="bullets-text"><p>If you want them to just forget you, is that even possible?</p></div>
        </div>
        <br>
        <p>Thanks to a new EU law, you can ask companies to provide you all your personal data. You can even ask them to delete all your data.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row div-margin-top" id="anchor-2">
      <div class="col-sm-6">
        <h1>How</h1>
        <h3> Getting your data is easy: </h3>
        <div class="bullets-flex">
          <div><i class="fa fa-circle bullets-icon"></i></div>
          <div class="bullets-text"><p>Select the companies whom you want to get your data from.</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="bullets-flex">
          <div><i class="fa fa-circle bullets-icon"></i></div>
          <div class="bullets-text"><p>Complete your profile. Upload your identification document.</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="bullets-flex">
          <div><i class="fa fa-circle bullets-icon"></i></div><div class="bullets-text"><p>Click on "send".</p></div>
        </div>
        <br>
        <p>Companies are obliged by law to respond within 30 days.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-sm-offset-1 col-sm-5">
        <%= image_tag "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1519389950473-47ba0277781c?ixlib=rb-0.3.5&ixid=eyJhcHBfaWQiOjEyMDd9&s=47d2b1f32cc05c976af4a39256e01cba&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1350&q=80", class: "home-image"  %>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row div-margin-top homepage-row" id="anchor-3">
      <div class="col-sm-12">
        <!-- Begin MailChimp Signup Form -->
        <div id="mc_embed_signup">
          <form action="https://getmydata.us12.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=1bdd45c5a52facc2466a07e44&amp;id=6a71f0cb3e" method="post" id="mc-embedded-subscribe-form" name="mc-embedded-subscribe-form" class="validate" target="_blank" novalidate>
            <div id="mc_embed_signup_scroll">
              <h3 class="text-center"> <h1 class="text-center">Stay up to date</h1> <h3 class="text-center">Subscribe to our mailing list</h3>
              <div class="mc-field-group text-center">
                <input style="width: 30%; height: 50px;" type="email" value="" name="EMAIL" class="required email text-center" id="mce-EMAIL" placeholder="Email">
              </div>
              <div id="mce-responses" class="clear">
                <div class="response" id="mce-error-response" style="display:none"></div>
                <div class="response" id="mce-success-response" style="display:none"></div>
              </div>    <!-- real people should not fill this in and expect good things - do not remove this or risk form bot signups-->
              <div style="margin-top: 20px;" class="clear text-center"><input type="submit" value="Subscribe" name="subscribe" id="mc-embedded-subscribe" class="button"></div>
            </div>
          </form>
        </div>

        <!--End mc_embed_signup-->
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
